<section
    id="futuro"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-future"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--narrow wheat-text-center">
        <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-future-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block wheat-mb-4">
            El Futuro
        </span>
        <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-8 wheat-future-title">El Trigo Infinito</h2>

        <div class="wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-gap-8 wheat-text-left wheat-mb-12">
            <div class="wheat-p-6 wheat-rounded wheat-border wheat-future-card">
                <h3 class="wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-future-card-title wheat-future-card-title--genetic wheat-mb-2">Edición Genética</h3>
                <p class="wheat-future-card-desc wheat-leading-relaxed">
                    Ya no esperamos mutaciones accidentales. Ahora reescribimos el código del trigo
                    para que sobreviva a la sequía, a la sal y al calor. El trigo del futuro no será
                    natural.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="wheat-p-6 wheat-rounded wheat-border wheat-future-card">
                <h3 class="wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-future-card-title wheat-future-card-title--vertical wheat-mb-2">Granjas Verticales</h3>
                <p class="wheat-future-card-desc wheat-leading-relaxed">
                    Liberar la tierra. Cultivar hacia arriba en torres de cristal en el centro de
                    las ciudades. El fin del agricultor, el inicio del ingeniero agrónomo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="wheat-text-xl wheat-text-2xl@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-future-quote wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto wheat-italic">
            "Empezamos domesticando una hierba salvaje. Terminamos domesticando el planeta entero
            para que le sirviera."
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-future {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-top: 1px solid #1c1917;
    }
    .wheat-future-chapter {
        color: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.6);
    }
    .wheat-future-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-future-card {
        background-color: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.5);
        border-color: #1c1917;
    }
    .wheat-future-card-title--genetic {
        color: #22c55e;
    }
    .wheat-future-card-title--vertical {
        color: #3b82f6;
    }
    .wheat-future-card-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-future-quote {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
</style>
